c180a3ee-5892-4ea4-aa31-fb58191ad59f.title: <player>
c180a3ee-5892-4ea4-aa31-fb58191ad59f.text: Why are you guys hanging around here?

9ac7903f-a92f-4faa-a0a7-e40f435f5e9d.title: <player>
9ac7903f-a92f-4faa-a0a7-e40f435f5e9d.text:
Uh... yeah, sorry about that. Why are you all standing
around out here?

6474e150-ed01-4fff-8e31-3b8c66577034.title: Archer
6474e150-ed01-4fff-8e31-3b8c66577034.text: Well, that's really none of your business.

b20244b3-65fe-4950-bee2-2b1ccdae226b.title: <player>
b20244b3-65fe-4950-bee2-2b1ccdae226b.text:
So I hear theres a leprechaun around here who can
show me the way to Zanaris?

f8e6c21b-d3e8-483d-9467-f91d16a9526a.title: Archer
f8e6c21b-d3e8-483d-9467-f91d16a9526a.text: No. You're wrong. Now go away.

5c9b1d15-350b-4d62-9b12-99121b60d814.title: <player>
5c9b1d15-350b-4d62-9b12-99121b60d814.text: So you didn't find the entrance to Zanaris yet, huh?

baac0d4f-1929-43fe-9211-241fa3e816fa.title: Archer
baac0d4f-1929-43fe-9211-241fa3e816fa.text: Don't tell me a novice like YOU has found it!

62bb7210-f0ab-4d02-9e97-a0b93f2ae426.title: <player>
62bb7210-f0ab-4d02-9e97-a0b93f2ae426.text: Yep. Found it REALLY easily too.

a52a72d7-dea0-4d45-a5bb-c65c6eb179c3.title: Archer
a52a72d7-dea0-4d45-a5bb-c65c6eb179c3.text:
...I cannot believe that someone like YOU could find the
portal where experienced adventurers such as ourselves
could not.

481b5eb6-6282-4da6-a069-26758d30b0e5.title: <player>
481b5eb6-6282-4da6-a069-26758d30b0e5.text: Believe what you want. Enjoy your little camp fire.
